    supports HTML5 video This is a modal window. Beginning of dialog window. Escape will cancel and close the window. End of dialog window.  Pule's uncle Tumisang Katake, who was one of the defence lawyers in Karabo Mokoena  murder case, said that he would no longer be representing rapist, molesters and killers. “Let her death not be the darkness upon our lives. Let her death be the bright and shining light in our lives and let it be the star that we look up to in the sky and we see the shining light when that star is shining bright,” he said. Katake also pleaded with the community of Meadowlands and South Africa to not take the law into their hands. To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
